    <description>Kubernetes TUI Debugger - One screen to see why your pod is broken.

k1s is a terminal-based user interface (TUI) for debugging Kubernetes workloads. It provides real-time logs, events, metrics, and resource inspection in a single dashboard view.

Features:
- Pod debugging dashboard with logs, events, and metrics
- Workload management (Deployments, StatefulSets, DaemonSets, Jobs, CronJobs)
- HPA viewing with CPU/Memory/External metrics
- ConfigMaps and Secrets viewer with clipboard support
- Cross-namespace resource copying
- Vim-style keyboard navigation
    </description>
